title: Here’s How Rani Mukerji Celebrated Her Birthday
text:
Divya Rao Mar . 23 . 2017 
Bollywood’s favourite bong beauty, Rani Mukerji , turned 39 yesterday and we almost had to pinch ourselves to believe it because she looks nothing close to it! The actress celebrated her birthday with her best girlfriends, Shanoo Sharma and Vaibhavi Merchant , yesterday and it looked like a lot of fun! Check out this photo. A post shared by Diwaah! (@shanoosharmarahihai) on Mar 21, 2017 at 3:22pm PDT 
How nice!
